# Concurrency-focused xfstests suite (2026-06-05)
#
# Dedicated suite gathering the concurrency / multi-process stress cases that
# were previously scattered across phase1/3/4/6 lists, plus new write-path
# concurrency stressors. Complements (does NOT replace) the self-developed
# deterministic multi-file data-integrity test in ext4_phase2/phase2_concurrency.c
# (fsstress-based xfstests check fs consistency but not byte-level data hash).
#
# Deliberately excluded cases (attrs / quota / dm-error) are documented with
# rationale in blocked/concurrency_excluded.tsv.

